# Solutions to type challenges

A repository for storing all my solutions to the **awesome** type challenges found on https://github.com/type-challenges/type-challenges.

The title of the challenge is a hyperlink to the TS playground with the full solution and tests, and below the title is just its solution.

#### [898 - Includes](https://www.typescriptlang.org/play#code/PQKgUABBAcCc0QLQQJIDsDGAbArgEwFMBnSJRci0gIwE8I0cssIAKAAQGsa0CAzHDgEoIAYgIBDInRHiATrPE0wpEaogBFHMQAuASwD2aZVBQBbAA5YCpgmm0RtACwIQAUuIBu4gMoZZu83sAAwBBeUUAOl1MXEIiIIh+TD1DCGiHZwcacxcpIm1rCIgQrJyHcQ5iDJdtAHd9CDkAcxwbOyIigBVM-Rxtcz6IIkderDwIKhdxCf19K3E0CCDtWS0E--yFerW4guu2uwIAG4E+9GkQ8LwQRAAN6NXWwiEsIQAAvpma65n++aFmgxb--iBFZ--Kiol7gKRoBX+qGjXdeWtasi2vawBEKX-cvBAHL-BsLiBvnTC2KJg9V0aJpEGaY+NxPjrOkAA)

```typescript
type Includes<T extends readonly any[], U> = 
  T extends [infer First, ...infer Rest] 
  ? Equal<First, U> extends true 
    ? true 
    : Includes<[...Rest], U> 
  : false
```

#### [9 - Deep readonly](https://www.typescriptlang.org/play#--qdEQeC2HJexmd81q+pg+k5gA-POuzyWZeyieJOg5JgBQ2QOWa6Qp+nIH6hnGeivCYgK-RzvZfneeOvl6QZcQhfMQwQHOUD2a5C7uTFT7pRA8X+WALY0XxvFnl4wx4kSJJlUxAlUUowQ+sMwmphA7YAI68J8aKAalVYQGI6gEGopZCMJcBQjCapeMAvA+CQ1iVmAbX2iSyZyZQ-WmDkXU9SQORZY595xvmBR9V2QyKOdF3bVdu37Z8R03tluRxgATBdHUPcBX13RpTirW2EBnVe-Z5oI0iJk+H0ffQWbeIkPyUMYWYQ1AeBZnQBAEKEog5iGY7jtE6P5ewZPjuOShZqw6iePlUAGGWSPGuuVOblTKn1jqJAEOzG5ziQWZbVze5rii+UY1zcgi+WjaA2LVaS1TiuC82xVCSDn3g5DrM-BAg0AD7tcuRCqMyvotm1O3Afm4MyW905ZgI0Ow-DE5O0uiN08ajsnTKlO5rJFrY7j+NEDmId1EHW5e6TxNU9HFOJ1z0c07c9PIIzDl3hAzMrvr0QCwOnNJ175g84q-NzmXwde8LueLqLXOrqWKtc9L5cB7LTdvHJ8sHmrHMdwOw+G5QNbWyDtuKB9uvRzOZK+wbxvtdHZsW10JUgDxdX0aF6gcF0ADKnRYXv+8NWAoCQRAJ-Qi8mq+uSJALdi2EQOhmHYbh1j4YRYi6hSLQGAKIawjx1B3xgnBMkeN348jQhhLCOFgB4XYARIiJEyLAFfggnEd8ACyPonh4hVLCWIn9v4oL-gArBwCKJUSAA)

```ts
type DeepReadonly<T> = {
  readonly [K in keyof T]: 
    T[K] extends [...infer R] 
    ? readonly [...DeepReadonly<R>] 
    : T[K] extends Function 
      ? T[K] 
      : T[K] extends object 
        ? DeepReadonly<T[K]> 
        : T[K]
```
